NEW: COMP 2 2 180 "buttons" 7 0 10
PART -1
ALPH 256 1
PART 0
POSE 0
PAT: BUTT 2 "demo1" 3 2 80 300 0 [1] 2001 1
PAT: BUTT 3 "demo1" 5 2 340 300 0 [1] 500 1
PAT: FIXD 4 "demo1" 7 25 80 0 "blackontransparentchars"
PART 4
FRMT 0 0 0 0 2 0 2
PTXT "**Welcome to the Demo of lifandi , an open source community game.*** 		 *******For more information see http://lifandi.ccdevnet.org .*****	    This demo is very simple demo , klick on 'ok' to get to the demoworld screen .***	            ."
SETV AVAR TARG 74 0
MVTO 1400 100
TICK 100
MESG WRT+ TARG 2000 0 0 0
TICK 40
SCRP 2 2 180 2001
CMRA 200 200 0
ENDM

SCRP 2 2 180 500

LOOP
ADDV VA00 32
PART -1
SETV VA01 VA00
ALPH VA01 1
WAIT 1
UNTL VA00 GT 256

WAIT 10
QUIT
KILL OWNR
ENDM

SCRP 2 2 180 2000
INST
LOCK
TICK 0
LOOP
LOCK
PART -1
SETV VA00 256
LOOP
SETV VA01 VA00
ALPH VA01 1
WAIT 0
SUBV VA00 1
UNTL VA00 LT 0

ALPH VA00 0
SETV AVAR OWNR 74 1
SETA VA02 OWNR
UNTL AVAR OWNR 74 NE 0

ENDM

RSCR
ENUM 2 2 180
KILL TARG

NEXT
SCRX 2 2 180 2000
SCRX 2 2 180 2001
SCRX 2 2 180 500
